name: theta
description: scattering angle in radians (0 = forward scattering direction)

name: real(S11)
description: real part of the parallel differential scattering cross section

name: imag(S11)
description: imaginary part of the parallel differential scattering cross section

name: real(S22)
description: real part of the perpendicular differential scattering cross section

name: imag(S22)
description: imaginary part of the perpendicular differential scattering cross section
